<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-13796] Salesforce Component IDLE_TIMEOUT Blocks Async Request Responses</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-13796</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Bulk, Composite Batch, etc. all throw an exception when trying to return on more than a few records due to &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-salesforce/camel-salesforce-component/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/salesforce/SalesforceComponent.java#L80&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;static final IDLE_TIMEOUT&lt;/a&gt; on the instantiated salesforce component httpClient:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Caused by: org.apache.camel.component.salesforce.api.SalesforceException: Unexpected error {0:null} executing {POST:&lt;a href=&quot;https://genericSFDCInstance.salesforce.com/services/data/v38.0/composite/batch&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://genericSFDCInstance.salesforce.com/services/data/v38.0/composite/batch&lt;/a&gt;}&lt;br/&gt;
