&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Note that as IDLE_TIMEOUT is static, it cannot be set via Spring, and the httpClientProperties map is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-salesforce/camel-salesforce-component/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/salesforce/SalesforceComponent.java#L714&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;never used to set any timeouts&lt;/a&gt;, instead opting to take the &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/master/components/camel-salesforce/camel-salesforce-component/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/salesforce/SalesforceComponent.java#L707&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;hardcoded defaults&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
